; .
;
; Four animation frames (1-byte header + 30 scanlines x 3 bytes each) used by
; #R39317 to animate the snake HUD when a fighter takes a hit. #R39367 sets the
; draw phase index in IY+7 bits 7-4 to 1 on impact; #R39317 advances
; .
; it each frame through the 14-step ping-pong cycle (phases 0-13) via the
; pointer table at #R47528, resetting to idle (0) when complete.
