; Barbarian sprite shape control table.
;
; 21 entries (0-20), 1 byte each. Defines shape/behaviour for each frame's
; sprite.
;
; .
;
; Accessed as (IX+0) by #R38367 (12-tile mirror checker). Controls tile grid
; expansion:
; .
; 255 = empty slot: INC IX (skip), no tile consumed from HL frame data. The
; rest IDs are active shape: consume 1 tile index from HL, render via #R37449.
; .
; Produces variable-width sprites: 0-3 tiles wide (4 rows tall), column offset
; follows.
