; Barbarian Spritesheet
;
; .
;
; .
;
; Frame data structure: 1-byte shape ID + 12 tile indices (4 rows x 3 tiles
; wide).
; .
; Shape table #R43520 defines sprite shapes; tile indices reference #R49152
; (barbarian tileset).
; .
; Rendered by #R37404 (4x3 grid blitter): loads column offset byte, then 12
; tiles via #R37449.
; .
; P2 uses identical base sprites as P1 with per-frame overlay tiles composited
; via #R38220.
; .
; #R47223: tile index per P2 frame (0-52, 255=no overlay). #R47329: position
; bits 0-5 scanline offset from row 94, bits 6-7 column offset (0-3 right of P2
; X tile, inverted if mirrored).
; .
; Overlay state #R46817 mirrors head block #R46809 layout, using shared
; renderer #R38103 + #R38158 orientation check.
; .
; #IMGW(50)(sprites_v3.png)
@label=barb_spritesheet
