; AI movement selection table.
;
; .
;
; .
;
; 23 blocks of 8 bytes. Block selected by profile[AI_state_col] x 8.
; .
; Within the block, sub_index (0-7) is chosen by the difficulty entry at
; #R47559[fight_counter], indexed by a random value (R AND 31).
; .
; Repeated movement IDs within a block adjust probability weighting.
; .
; Movement 0 = do-nothing/idle this decision.
; .
; Lower block IDs (0-7) = passive/defensive mix.
; .
; Higher block IDs (9-22) = increasingly aggressive.
@label=ai_movement_table
b47974 DEFB 25,21,22,26,20,24,0,17 ;  Block 0:  [25,21,22,26,20,24, 0,17]
                                   ; varied mix
 47982 DEFB 22,20,26,24,17,20,22,0 ;  Block 1:  [22,20,26,24,17,20,22, 0]
                                   ; walk/approach mix
 47990 DEFB 20,1,1,26,26,1,0,0     ;  Block 2:  [20, 1, 1,26,26, 1, 0, 0]
                                   ; mostly passive
 47998 DEFB 18,18,26,26,1,1,0,0    ;  Block 3:  [18,18,26,26, 1, 1, 0, 0]
                                   ; passive/retreat
 48006 DEFB 1,5,1,1,1,1,1,1        ;  Block 4:  [ 1, 5, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
                                   ; mostly fwd+attack-5
 48014 DEFB 5,5,5,5,2,2,2,0        ;  Block 5:  [ 5, 5, 5, 5, 2, 2, 2, 0]
                                   ; attack-5 dominant
 48022 DEFB 5,5,5,5,1,1,0,1        ;  Block 6:  [ 5, 5, 5, 5, 1, 1, 0, 1]
                                   ; attack-5 dominant
 48030 DEFB 26,20,26,20,5,6,4,0    ;  Block 7:  [26,20,26,20, 5, 6, 4, 0]
                                   ; approach+attack mix
 48038 DEFB 1,5,1,1,1,1,1,1        ;  Block 8:  [ 1, 5, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]  same
                                   ; as block 4
 48046 DEFB 8,8,2,2,6,4,2,0        ;  Block 9:  [ 8, 8, 2, 2, 6, 4, 2, 0]
                                   ; heavy attack
 48054 DEFB 25,25,9,9,9,9,9,0      ;  Block 10: [25,25, 9, 9, 9, 9, 9, 0]
                                   ; attack-9 dominant
